To compile the simulator for the C54:

cd c54
make

Note: you'll need to have gtk+extra. Download from http://gtkextra.sourceforge.net/

To analyze a file.
./gdspsim -f filename


To compile the simulator for the C55
cd c55
make

The C55 port still needs alot of work.


KNOWN BUGS

The plot axes don't update unless you move the plot.

The file IO needs more work.



